{"tid":2296660,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"唔識物理, 純好奇想知","createTime":"2020-11-22T16:11:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T16:44:39.000Z","uid":149829,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"93e39d191e9386b555abbdf348d1e1c6c660047d","tid":2296660,"uid":149829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T16:11:04.000Z","msg":"&quot;廣義相對論：根據廣義相對論，引力會對時間產生影響，越高的地方時鐘走得越快。人造衛星距離地面大約2萬千米，因此衛星里的原子鐘比在地球上的原子鐘每天要快45微秒&quot;<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://kknews.cc/science/z63j4nl.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fscience%2Fz63j4nl.html&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT8g7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=cea9b739\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/science/z63j4nl.html</a><br />\n<br />\n我想問重力要去到幾多時間先會比地球每日慢一秒?"},{"pid":"eb7cdebb30c86467e66f10a9303cd8cc3aa686bf","tid":2296660,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T16:38:19.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"78851b93efe07966f812babd8c5b3266fa9fc31c","tid":2296660,"uid":22302,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T19:46:10.000Z","msg":"假設個星球同地球一樣大（同埋假設我無計錯數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n如果地球表面過左86400秒既時候呢個星球既表面過左86399秒，咁佢既質量要係9.95*10^28 kg，佢表面既重力加速度係1.64*10^5 m/s^2 (地球16000幾倍)<br />\n<br />\n地球表面過左86400秒既話，太陽表面大約比地球少左183秒"},{"pid":"138e3669323b0782c003ff635de306cc76cabb20","tid":2296660,"uid":323922,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"93e39d191e9386b555abbdf348d1e1c6c660047d","tid":2296660,"uid":149829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T16:11:04.000Z","msg":"&quot;廣義相對論：根據廣義相對論，引力會對時間產生影響，越高的地方時鐘走得越快。人造衛星距離地面大約2萬千米，因此衛星里的原子鐘比在地球上的原子鐘每天要快45微秒&quot;<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://kknews.cc/science/z63j4nl.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fscience%2Fz63j4nl.html&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT8g7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=cea9b739\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/science/z63j4nl.html</a><br />\n<br />\n我想問重力要去到幾多時間先會比地球每日慢一秒?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T20:05:50.000Z","msg":"每外太空一秒，地表行sqrt(1-2GM/rc^2)秒<br />\n<br />\nsqrt = 平方根 (square root)<br />\nG = 6.674 X 10^-11 m^3 kg^-1 s^-2<br />\nM = 腳底下有幾多kg物質，地球重5.97 X 10^24 kg<br />\nr = 你距離地心幾多米(m)，地球半徑6.378 X 10^6 m<br />\nc = 3 X 10^8 m s^-1<br />\n一日慢幾多秒乘番：24小時乘3600秒<br />\n<br />\n另外，地表地心吸力係g = 9.8 m s^-2 = GM/r^2<br />\n<br />\n可以自己計下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63e4bef4434a4257541344d8704d3629f1358b33","tid":2296660,"uid":323922,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T20:27:15.000Z","msg":"另外，衛星速度可以用v^2/r = GM/r^2黎計，衛星速度(v)係 =  GM/r<br />\nG 同M同上，呢度r係衛星離地心既速度。靜止觀察每行一秒，衛星行1/sqrt(1-v^2/c^2)秒<br />\n<br />\nc同上係光速。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68c9bde6e03947729be1e6e821581829d2e1e5f","tid":2296660,"uid":28763,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T20:30:05.000Z","msg":"睇埋d content farm 做乜"},{"pid":"d2e1feaefb23e94b821d47c6209470c67f7d2588","tid":2296660,"uid":263025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93e39d191e9386b555abbdf348d1e1c6c660047d","tid":2296660,"uid":149829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T16:11:04.000Z","msg":"&quot;廣義相對論：根據廣義相對論，引力會對時間產生影響，越高的地方時鐘走得越快。人造衛星距離地面大約2萬千米，因此衛星里的原子鐘比在地球上的原子鐘每天要快45微秒&quot;<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://kknews.cc/science/z63j4nl.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fscience%2Fz63j4nl.html&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT8g7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=cea9b739\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/science/z63j4nl.html</a><br />\n<br />\n我想問重力要去到幾多時間先會比地球每日慢一秒?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T20:36:06.000Z","msg":"壓住你行唔喐既重力"},{"pid":"fe43bf2ab032a9ae4256af5be041ec11c6c75726","tid":2296660,"uid":295602,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T20:42:51.000